OL,3,CConcern over vermin infestation in
OL,4,Chospital kitchen
OL,6,FA vermin infestation found in a
OL,7,Fhospital kitchen, where patient and
OL,8,Fstaff meals are prepared, has sparked
OL,9,Fconcerns over health and safety.
OL,11,FUTV can reveal that pest controllers
OL,12,Fhad to be called in to Craigavon Area
OL,13,FHospital after droppings were
OL,14,Fdiscovered over work benches and
OL,15,Ffloors in the main kitchen and dining
OL,16,Farea.
OL,18,FThe Southern Health Trust said the
OL,19,Frecent pest sighting was "dealt with
OL,20,Fquickly and all the usual procedures
OL,21,Fwere followed".
