OL,3,CConcern over vermin infestation in
OL,4,Chospital kitchen
OL,6,FHowever hospital staff say they are
OL,7,Fconcerned the rodents may return, as
OL,8,Fthey are struggling with staff
OL,9,Fshortages.
OL,11,F"Those droppings were found over
OL,12,Futensils and surfaces. Pest
OL,13,Fcontrollers came in last Friday along
OL,14,Fwith high level cleaners," hospital
OL,15,Fworker John Creaney told UTV.
OL,17,FHe added: "I was horrified. That
OL,18,Fkitchen is where food is prepared for
OL,19,Fpatients and staff. Everyone is
OL,20,Fworried this will happen again."
